Rebuild the file index

Usage: moss index rebuild [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --include <INCLUDE>
          What to extract: symbols, calls, imports (default: all)

          Possible values:
          - none:    Skip content extraction (files only)
          - symbols: Function and type definitions
          - calls:   Function call relationships
          - imports: Import statements
          
          [default: symbols calls imports]

  -r, --root <ROOT>
          Root directory (defaults to current directory)

      --json
          Output as JSON

      --jq <EXPR>
          Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)

      --pretty
          Human-friendly output with colors and formatting

      --compact
          Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
